title: U.S. women who have given oral sex to a male in their lifetime , by age group
summary: This is a bar chart representing Age group in the x axis and Share of respondents in the y axis.
The maximum Share of respondents 89.0 is found at Age group 25-29 and the minimum is found at 14-15 where Age group is 13.0.
The difference of Share of respondents between the highest and lowest Age group is 76.0.
